text: Kittu Suresh (27 February 1945 - 6 January 2010) was an Indian cricketer who played in twenty-three first-class matches for Mysore between 1966 and 1972. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1945 births Category:2010 deaths Category:Indian cricketers Category:Karnataka cricketers Category:Place of birth missing
title: Kittu Suresh
